{"tid":739876,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本女性感染梅毒數字飆升","createTime":"2018-07-12T12:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T12:07:31.000Z","uid":141837,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c584238ed635a457fe6ebf59f8bd4c51aebad348","tid":739876,"uid":141837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:05:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180712/s00005/1531391343734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180712%2Fs00005%2F1531391343734&d=igWnFcSndmnKNssnHbQb01KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=e13b1d36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180712%2Fs00005%2F1531391343734&h=58d34e1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180712/s00005/1531391343734</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日本傳媒報道，近年感染梅毒的女性人數飆升</span>。專家相信，是跟科技發展迅速，透過<span style=\"color: red;\">社交網絡衍生的性交易行業</span>增加有關。<br />\n<br />\n日本當地近年感染梅毒的女性人數大幅上升，從1990年起每年約1000人以下感染，2013年已突破1200人，2015年倍增至2650人。到2017年，感染人數已超過5000人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">患病的人以25歲以下的年輕女性居多，15到35歲的女性佔76%，尤其家庭主婦人數也不斷上升</span>，大部分婦人都是在剛懷孕或準備生產時感染。孕婦若不慎感染梅毒又沒有治療，流產機會率達40%，胎兒也有60至80%機會受感染。<br />\n<br />\n根據本港衛生防議中心資料，梅毒病菌是梅毒螺旋菌，潛伏期約9天至90天，大部分病人在接觸病菌後2至4個星期發病。<br />\n<br />\n（朝日新聞）"},{"pid":"d8a39db9f9b254d091ede7454c0bf42b6383cd0a","tid":739876,"uid":6959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e43fbbb6a33919b24a1f946327f0274d09b9d00","tid":739876,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T12:07:31.000Z","msg":"日本結左婚果d女人係咪好鐘意出軌<br />\n睇晝顏睇上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}